{"tid":970852,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"驗基因測孩子天賦 專家稱不準 收費4萬 公司回應準確度：先天後天五十五十","createTime":"2019-01-06T07:41:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-06T10:34:41.000Z","uid":229553,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4c2e72d24d8dfe44c8e5922cb717e74c92a14e8e","tid":970852,"uid":229553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T07:41:57.000Z","msg":"痴L線<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來依家嘅錢咁好賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一次4皮野<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但又話50/50<br />\n<br />\n測基因分析天賦的貴價服務正打入家長市場，有家長甚至要求公立醫院為孩子測天賦。但有「基因獵人」之稱的港大專家林青雲，檢閱一份收費4萬元、為4歲兒童檢測的報告後，指人類智力受近2000條基因影響，科學界尚未找出IQ（智商）基因，認為準確度「很低」。提供該測試的geneDecode則稱現已發現控制智力的基因，但以保密為由拒絕提供，並就其準確度回應稱先天與後天「永遠都是五十五十」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20190106/s00001/1546711638351/%E9%A9%97%E5%9F%BA%E5%9B%A0%E6%B8%AC%E5%AD%A9%E5%AD%90%E5%A4%A9%E8%B3%A6-%E5%B0%88%E5%AE%B6%E7%A8%B1%E4%B8%8D%E6%BA%96-%E6%94%B6%E8%B2%BB4%E8%90%AC-%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E6%BA%96%E7%A2%BA%E5%BA%A6-%E5%85%88%E5%A4%A9%E5%BE%8C%E5%A4%A9%E4%BA%94%E5%8D%81%E4%BA%94%E5%8D%81\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190106%2Fs00001%2F1546711638351%2F%25E9%25A9%2597%25E5%259F%25BA%25E5%259B%25A0%25E6%25B8%25AC%25E5%25AD%25A9%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E8%25B3%25A6-%25E5%25B0%2588%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25BA%2596-%25E6%2594%25B6%25E8%25B2%25BB4%25E8%2590%25AC-%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258F%25B8%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2587%2589%25E6%25BA%2596%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E5%25BA%25A6-%25E5%2585%2588%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E5%25BE%258C%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E4%25BA%2594%25E5%258D%2581%25E4%25BA%2594%25E5%258D%2581&d=X4%2FzfWi5cbJ7qy%2BCoL4PzTQ9OVC7k%2Fvddp